{"tid":1392712,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"庵野秀明製作真人版《咸蛋超人》","createTime":"2019-07-31T23:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T12:46:52.000Z","uid":41343,"like":10,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"71160f6fadfc692d3851acef2e8dcf00637f5555","tid":1392712,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T23:58:48.000Z","msg":"前陣子關於庵野秀明將主導新版超人力霸王電影的謠言,在今日於庵野秀明的動畫公司Khara以及日本各大媒體被證實了！<br />\n《新&middot;超人力霸王》（シン・ウルトラマン）的企劃和劇本都會由庵野秀明負責,導演則由樋口真嗣出任<br />\n<br />\n演員則有西島秀俊、長澤雅美,超人力霸王的人間體由齊藤工飾演,三位演員的角色都會是隸屬應對巨大生物的組織成員<br />\n<br />\n劇情走向會如同2016年的《真哥斯拉》,以現實社會真的出現巨大生物與超人會發生什麼事為主題發展,並且會參考實相寺昭雄這位已故超人力霸王系列導演的特殊風格拍攝<br />\n<br />\n該片會由Kahara、圓谷、東寶三家公司共同製作,並由東寶影業負責發行,預定於2021年上映<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20190801-00000005-spnannex-ent\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadlines.yahoo.co.jp%2Fhl%3Fa%3D20190801-00000005-spnannex-ent&d=puaUx2dgpXXsrsLU9noyGC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=e52c51e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/hl?a=20190801-00000005-spnannex-ent</a>"},{"pid":"0cddb87a9604b73413d6a1df6be04af51c0414f4","tid":1392712,"uid":196924,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:02:40.000Z","msg":"好心標題講明係電影<br />\nUltraman本身就係真人特攝乜鳩嘢真人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb12c1671a40f7d5c58c229a0d170109326d7d06","tid":1392712,"uid":28397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0cddb87a9604b73413d6a1df6be04af51c0414f4","tid":1392712,"uid":196924,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T00:02:40.000Z","msg":"好心標題講明係電影<br />\nUltraman本身就係真人特攝乜鳩嘢真人版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T01:52:19.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hk